  "text": "Assessment of housing conditions was measured by the interviewer's subjective ratings at the baseline interview of the cleanliness inside the building, physical condition of the interior, condition of furnishings, condition of the exterior of the building, and a global rating (all rated as excellent, good, fair, or poor). The testretest reliability was at least 0.68 for each condition. [CITATION_1] In the present analysis, each block face condition and each housing condition were dichotomized as either fair or poor versus good or excellent.",
